title: Tim Cook Doesn’t Want You to See This

author: More Perfect Union
description:
There’s a new wave of predatory lenders on the market.

Though “cash-advance" apps talk about fighting big banks, they make millions off of outrageous APR and hidden fees.

Some borrowers are paying 4-figure interest rates — but these fintech companies still ask for a tip.
